metadata.name: LIGHTNING IN THE DOLOMITES
metadata.description:
This picture was taken in the Dolomites when we wanted to reach the Schlegeis Stausee bridge at the top of the mountain. After 1 hour trekking in the rain we got stuck in a storm and we had to stop at a refuge to spend the night there. We finally left the refuge the morning after to access the bridge and we had the chance to take this incredible lightning shot !


2594x3243 pixels
